text: Mikko Lahtela (born October 19, 1992) is a Finnish ice hockey player. He is currently playing with Lahti Pelicans in the Finnish Liiga. Lahtela made his Liiga debut playing with Lahti Pelicans during the 2014–15 Liiga season. ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Finnish ice hockey forwards Category:Lahti Pelicans players
